window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A winter weekend ends in snowbound disaster in a novel which remains a favourite among Marsh readers. </p> <p>It began as an entertainment: eight people, many of them enemies, gathered for a winter weekend by a host with a love for theatre. They would be the characters in a drama that he would devise. </p> <p>It ended in snowbound disaster. Everyone had an alibi - and most had motives as well. But Chief Detective Inspector Roderick Alleyn, when he finally arrived, knew it all hung on Thomas, the dancing footman.... </p>"; 
